{"type":"message","id":"756a806a","parentId":"7e848276","timestamp":"2026-03-09T20:51:20.637Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_BS2GHII4tpCq7NajK3NBGN8T|fc_0a7b28860b6f9d620169af32b6bfe88191996e7f319b75b67b","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"dict_keys(['status', 'metadata', 'data'])\nstatus= 200\nmetadata= {'name': 'AutoGen-model', 'type': 'ai_tool.AutoGen-model', 'run_id': 'debug', 'workflow_name': 'OpenClaw Pipeline Generator', 'workflow_type': 'prototype', 'workflow_id': '15657162-4ef2-4e04-8326-bf54e71ec6a2', 'workflow_run_id': '15657162-4ef2-4e04-8326-bf54e71ec6a2'}\ndata type= dict\ndata keys= dict_keys(['Answer', 'Perplexity Score', 'ImageBase64'])\nANSWER_START\nNode Explanation:\n\n*   **Image Reader:** This node is responsible for loading the image file. It handles various image formats and prepares the image data for subsequent processing.\n*   **Text Cleaner:** This node is used to clean any associated text data, such as metadata or descriptions related to the image. This ensures that any textual information is properly formatted and free of errors.\n*   **Skin Cancer Detection:** This is the core model node. It utilizes a pre-trained or fine-tuned model to analyze the image and identify potential signs of skin cancer.\n*   **Confusion Matrix Calculator:** This node evaluates the performance of the `Skin Cancer Detection` model by calculating the confusion matrix. This matrix provides insights into the model's accuracy, precision, recall, and other relevant metrics.\n*   **PDF File Exporter:** This node generates a PDF report containing the analysis results, including the model's predictions, confidence scores, and the evaluation metrics from the confusion matrix. This report provides a comprehensive overview of the skin cancer detection process.\nANSWER_END\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"dawn-lobster","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"dict_keys(['status', 'metadata', 'data'])\nstatus= 200\nmetadata= {'name': 'AutoGen-model', 'type': 'ai_tool.AutoGen-model', 'run_id': 'debug', 'workflow_name': 'OpenClaw Pipeline Generator', 'workflow_type': 'prototype', 'workflow_id': '15657162-4ef2-4e04-8326-bf54e71ec6a2', 'workflow_run_id': '15657162-4ef2-4e04-8326-bf54e71ec6a2'}\ndata type= dict\ndata keys= dict_keys(['Answer', 'Perplexity Score', 'ImageBase64'])\nANSWER_START\nNode Explanation:\n\n*   **Image Reader:** This node is responsible for loading the image file. It handles various image formats and prepares the image data for subsequent processing.\n*   **Text Cleaner:** This node is used to clean any associated text data, such as metadata or descriptions related to the image. This ensures that any textual information is properly formatted and free of errors.\n*   **Skin Cancer Detection:** This is the core model node. It utilizes a pre-trained or fine-tuned model to analyze the image and identify potential signs of skin cancer.\n*   **Confusion Matrix Calculator:** This node evaluates the performance of the `Skin Cancer Detection` model by calculating the confusion matrix. This matrix provides insights into the model's accuracy, precision, recall, and other relevant metrics.\n*   **PDF File Exporter:** This node generates a PDF report containing the analysis results, including the model's predictions, confidence scores, and the evaluation metrics from the confusion matrix. This report provides a comprehensive overview of the skin cancer detection process.\nANSWER_END\n","name":"python3 <<'PY'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773089480622}}
